Comparison: Behavioral Patterns at a Glance
Pattern	Key Utility
Observer	Keeps multiple objects in sync with a subject.
Strategy	Swaps different versions of an algorithm.
Command	Encapsulates an action as an object (supports Undo).
State	Changes behavior based on internal status.
Chain of Responsibility	Passes a request through a series of potential handlers.
Mediator	Centralizes communication between components.


